<div id="banner">
	<h1>Noam on Terrorism</h1>
</div>

<div class="content">
<p>Noam Chomsky: <a href="http://www.zmag.org/GlobalWatch/chomskymit.htm">The New War Against Terrorism</a>. Chomsky is the kind of person who is so eminently reasonable that you can&#8217;t help but agree with what he writes. But then you realize how far he is from the rest of the population and you wonder what&#8217;s happened to the world today.</p>

<p>Also check out <a href="http://monkeyfist.com/ChomskyArchive">Bad News: Noam Chomsky Archive</a>.</p>

